{"tid":773142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【癡肥病毒】感染後脂肪細胞「不死」 美專家研減肥疫苗","createTime":"2018-08-09T09:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T14:21:11.000Z","uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"562ce969f2526fd7f03128eef4368e234b89bff4","tid":773142,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:45:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180807/58528678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F58528678&d=4HARd12Fs2HlhsTp1kULoY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b959f366\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F58528678&h=2cd0ba7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180807/58528678</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你一直努力減肥但也瘦不下來，可能和一種叫「腺病毒-36」（Adenovirus-36）的病毒有關。美國最新有研究發現，癡肥女性體內有此病毒的機率較體重正常的女性高出4倍，而此病毒能令脂肪細胞「不死」不斷積聚，有專家更已開始研製疫苗並申請專利，冀日後「一針解決肥胖問題」。<br />\n<br />\n研究指，「腺病毒-36」可以傳染，它會刺激脂肪細胞使其發炎，令脂肪細胞「不死」，更妨礙它們排出體外，令脂肪積聚引起肥胖。研究亦發現，「腺病毒-36」能使動物的體重增加多達15%。<br />\n<br />\n麻省大學專家韋伯利博士（Dr Wilmore Webley）對比超重的與體重正常的乳癌女病人的健康身體組織，發現在前者體內找到「腺病毒-36」的機率達80%，比起後者的20%高出4倍，雖然癌症可能令細胞更易感染，但早前已有研究發現，猴子注入該病毒後會增重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n威斯康辛大學的榮譽教授艾堅遜博士（Dr Richard Atkinson）稱，他正研發一隻可對抗「腺病毒-36」的疫苗，並已申請專利。他指已有南韓學者在動物身上測試疫苗，成功令脂肪細胞免受「腺病毒-36」感染，唯仍未能籌集足夠資金將疫苗推出巿場。<br />\n<br />\n不過有專家不看好，倫敦大學學院專門研究肥胖問題的專家芬納（Nick Finer）指，「腺病毒-36」與體重上升的關係，仍有待進一步研究證明，他說：「無論多少研究指出兩者有關聯，但仍未能證明兩者的因果關係。」<br />\n<br />\n英國國家肥胖論壇主席賴伊（Tam Fry）也認為疫苗仍需進行更多測試，現階段來說，健康的飲食和運動習慣才是減肥的王道。"},{"pid":"c754814f10aaaf888b1c9f8a286dcd2183b76f3f","tid":773142,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #catgirl #princejoyce"},{"pid":"71a276318a2771a6a5518545f17a0c07aded9c95","tid":773142,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"又有得賴喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3360a49978027e5365896b78a27940a380c7a168","tid":773142,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3238a8b3234691d9362c65dd96aaff9e1e62962","tid":773142,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb4ec03fd79c6c863c188d03de2c00efc2641f9","tid":773142,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"原來肥唔係原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f64880556087548013b7e94d7474be04e578228","tid":773142,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T14:21:11.000Z","msg":"欣宜又多個理由唔減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}